1.1.name: wordpress/expresspigeon-webform-widget
1.1.description:
The ExpressPigeon Subscription Form allows you to easily add a newsletter subscription form to your Wordpress blog or site without any coding.

If you want to experience ExpressPigeon, simply register for FREE

ExpressPigeon is an email marketing system that is flexible, easy to use and requires no coding, like this plugin!
